@startuml
title Issue Prescription - Sequence Design
autonumber
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Veterinarian" as Vet
participant "Web SPA" as Web
participant "api-gateway" as Gateway
participant "visits-service\nPrescriptionController" as Controller
participant "PrescriptionService" as Service
participant "PrescriptionPdfGenerator" as Pdf
participant "files-service / MinIO" as Files
database "visits schema" as DB
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ

Vet -> Web: Add medication lines and instructions
Web -> Gateway: POST /api/v1/visits/{id}/prescriptions
Gateway -> Controller: route with VET JWT
Controller -> Service: issuePrescription(visitId, request)
Service -> DB: load visit and validate assigned vet
Service -> DB: save Prescription + items
Service -> Pdf: generate PDF
Pdf --> Service: PDF bytes
Service -> Files: upload prescription PDF
Files --> Service: objectKey / file reference
Service -> DB: attach PDF metadata
Service -> MQ: publish PrescriptionIssuedEvent
Controller --> Web: PrescriptionResponse
@enduml
